         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>On this auspicious day of the year called Siddhārtthin, month of Puṟaṭṭāci, 8th day,
               Thursday, the eleventh [lunar day that ends at the] 55th [hour], [constellation of]
               Puṣyaṃ [that ends at the] 56th [hour], Tūppil Rāghavadāsaṉ completed the
               Prayogadarpaṇam. Knowing this, one should be favourable.</p>
         </div>
